    Dropdown aligned to the right side of the container. To align dropdown to right, you have to add
    <code class="format-code">.wds-is-right-aligned</code> class to
    <code class="format-code">.wds-dropdown__content</code> element or (in Ember Component) add
    <code class="format-code">dropdownRightAligned=true</code>
    to the dropdown.content component.
  </p>
  <Demo @name="dropdown-right">
